{"tid":117283,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩食譚仔見到既奇人奇事","createTime":"2017-02-12T05:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T03:37:19.000Z","uid":71102,"like":273,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"857c2465dfec9900be45a31dd19dcb2eb90e1e7a","tid":117283,"uid":71102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩一枝公去食譚仔<br />\n太多人等位所以要搭枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟一如既往<br />\n嗌左碗米線同凍奶茶<br />\n然後仲嗌左碟大既土匪雞翼添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正當我嗌完既時候<br />\n同枱6個人都開始點餐<br />\n佢地嗌左一碗過橋米線同兩碗淨米線<br />\n再加左份12蚊特價小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望一望張單，佢地用100蚊餵飽6個人<br />\n（五個大人同一個初小小學雞）<br />\n我再望下自己張單，盛惠73蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我既土豪雞翼上枱既時候<br />\n佢地好似深受吸引<br />\n於是又嗌左一碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦，一碟大土豪雞翼得5隻，點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n答案係，成班食米線面不改容既大人<br />\n個個咬啖土豪雞翼就係咁嗌好辣啊<br />\n然後同小學雞講，太辣啦你食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9dc8a0f46d87d85e81fbe14fb14fee7d1bbfb7","tid":117283,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5710ff81e8000d604a0c003aa915d55e556d3f6d","tid":117283,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5587df0aeb43da8996f7949fd0b36787105305c2","tid":117283,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"咁濕尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"